---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Student Utility Hub"
  description="Read the Terms and Conditions of use for the Student Utility Hub calculators."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-4 py-16 sm:py-24 md:px-6 animate-fade-in-up">
    <nav class="mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-1.5 body-sm text-mute">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">Home</a></li>
        <li aria-hidden="true">/</li>
        <li class="text-ink font-medium">Terms & Conditions</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="display-lg text-ink mb-6">Terms & Conditions.</h1>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 body-md text-body">
      <p><em>Last updated: October 2024</em></p>

      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>Student Utility Hub</strong>. By accessing or using our website, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="body-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">1. Use of the Calculators</h2>
        <p>
          Student Utility Hub provides various academic calculators (SGPA, CGPA, percentage, attendance). These tools are provided for informational and planning purposes only. While we strive for accuracy, the results generated by our calculators do not constitute official academic records.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="body-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">2. Accuracy of Information</h2>
        <p>
          Different universities and educational boards have unique formulas and rounding rules. We provide customizable multipliers to accommodate these differences, but <strong>it is your responsibility to verify your final grades and percentages with your official university administration or marksheets.</strong> We accept no liability for discrepancies between our calculations and official university results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="body-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">3. User Responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          The website and its tools are provided "as-is". You agree to use the platform at your own risk. Student Utility Hub shall not be held liable for any academic or professional consequences arising from reliance on the calculations provided on this site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="body-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The layout, design, and source code of Student Utility Hub are subject to intellectual property rights. You may not scrape, clone, or republish our interactive calculators on other domains without explicit permission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="body-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">5. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions regarding these terms, please reach out to <a href="mailto:support@studentutilityhub.com" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">support@studentutilityhub.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
